    {
      "id": "p002",
      "index": 2,
      "source": "Broadcom showcased progress on their 6.4T MZM optical engine (OE) consisting of 64 lanes of ~100G using PAM4 modulation. The optical engines were tested in a Tomahawk 5 51.2T CPO system. One CPO package consists of eight 6.4T OEs, each with a PIC and an EIC, on TSMC’s N7 process.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0243",
      "parent_block_index": 243,
      "parent_block_type": "p",
      "parent_block_markdown": "Broadcom showcased progress on their 6.4T MZM optical engine (OE) consisting of 64 lanes of ~100G using PAM4 modulation. The optical engines were tested in a Tomahawk 5 51.2T CPO system. One CPO package consists of eight 6.4T OEs, each with a PIC and an EIC, on TSMC’s N7 process.",
      "parent_block_plain_text": "Broadcom showcased progress on their 6.4T MZM optical engine (OE) consisting of 64 lanes of ~100G using PAM4 modulation. The optical engines were tested in a Tomahawk 5 51.2T CPO system. One CPO package consists of eight 6.4T OEs, each with a PIC and an EIC, on TSMC’s N7 process.",
      "parent_source_html": null,
      "parent_inline_elements": [],
      "segment_start": 0,
      "segment_end": 280,
      "expected_tokens": [],
      "format_recovery_status": "not_applicable",
      "format_errors": [],
      "is_heading": false,
      "heading_level": null,
      "heading_chain": [],
      "is_metadata": false,
      "metadata_type": null,
      "translations": {
        "pro": {
          "text": "博通展示了其 6.4T MZM（马赫-曾德尔调制器）光学引擎的进展。该光学引擎由 64 条通道组成，每条通道速率约 100G，采用 PAM4（四电平脉冲幅度调制）调制。这些光学引擎在 Tomahawk 5 51.2T CPO（共封装光学）系统中进行了测试。一个 CPO 封装包含八个 6.4T 光学引擎，每个引擎均由一个光子集成电路和一个电子集成电路组成，采用台积电 N7 工艺制造。",
          "model": "pro",
          "created_at": "2026-04-18T01:36:55.780262",
          "tokenized_text": null,
          "format_issues": []
        }
      },
