      "id": "p005",
      "index": 5,
      "source": "While Nvidia uses COUPE, Broadcom uses a Fan-Out Wafer-Level Packaging approach for this OE. Broadcom will be switching to COUPE in the future, but older generation products like this OE still use other supply chain partners. Here are the promising results from their demonstration:",
